trans-unit.source: Represents the enumerator on the collection.
trans-unit.target: Stellt den Enumerator für die Auflistung dar.

trans-unit.source: The following example enumerates through all of the instances of the **Win32_LogicalDisk** class, and displays the **DeviceID** value for each instance.
